      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a purist\u2019s specification featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example exhibits the sharp throttle response inherent to its individual throttle bodies and maintains a tight, communicative chassis. Essential preventive maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a valve clearance adjustment. The rear subframe has been inspected for stress fractures and remains structurally sound. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust, benefiting from a recent fluid service and refreshed bushings. It is a highly capable driver\u2019s car that delivers a visceral 8,000 RPM redline experience and precise handling via the factory limited-slip differential.",
